ission%20announced%20the%20poll%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20goes%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2023.%20The%20votes%20for%20the%20200-seat%20assembly%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20seven%20MPs%20and%20the%20seats%20they%20will%20contest%20from%20are%3A%20Diya%20Kumari%20(Vidhyadhar%20Nagar)%2C%20Bhagirath%20Choudhary%20(Kishangarh)%2C%20Kirodi%20Lal%20Meena%20(Sawai%20Madhopur)%2C%20Devji%20Patel%20(Sanchore)%2C%20Narendra%20Kumar%20(Mandawa)%2C%20Rajyavardhan%20Rathore%20(Jhotwara)%20and%20Baba%20Balaknath%20(Tijara).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20is%20a%20careful%20mix%20of%20caste%20and%20regional%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECol%20Kirori%20Singh%20Bainsla's%20son%20Vijay%20bainsla%20has%20been%20given%20a%20ticket.%20His%20father%20Col%20Bainsla%20launched%20the%20reservation%20movement%20for%20Gujjars%2C%20which%20is%20still%20an%20emotive%20issue%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20gave%20tickets%20to%20nine%20Gujjars.%20However%2C%20all%20of%20them%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKirodi%20Lal%20Meena%2C%20a%20big%20draw%20to%20pull%20in%20Meena%20votes%2C%20has%20also%20been%20pulled%20into%20the%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20were%20finalised%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20party's%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20(CEC)%20that%20was%20chaired%20by%20the%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20on%20October%201.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20also%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20PM%20Modi%20gave%20a%20clear%20indication%20that%20no%20leader%20will%20be%20projected%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20The%20party%20symbol%20'lotus'%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20candidate%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%2C%20infighting%20and%20power%20tussle%20within%20the%20ranks%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20key%20challenge%20as%20the%20party%20readies%20for%20the%20polls.%20Infighting%20is%20a%20key%20challenge%20for%20the%20BJP%20too%2C%20with%20rival%20camps%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20jostling%20with%20each%20other%20for%20prominence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20three%20Union%20Ministers%20-%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20-%20and%20four%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20as%20candidates%20for%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20will%20see%20a%20direct%20fight%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20-%20anti-incumbency%20is%20an%20important%20factor.%20Since%201993%2C%20the%20state%20has%20alternated%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2099%20of%20the%20199%20seats%20where%20elections%20were%20held%20(polling%20in%20one%20constituency%20was%20cancelled%20because%20of%20a%20candidate's%20death).%20The%20BJP%20won%2073.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696853820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fqfus6pig_bjp-supporters-bjp-flag-reuters_625x300_01_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F7-mps-among-bjps-first-list-of-41-candidates-for-rajasthan-polls-4464335%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seven%20MPs%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20first%20list%20of%2041%20candidates%20by%20BJP%20for%20the%20Rajasthan%20elections%2C%20just%20hours%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20the%20poll%20dates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F7-mps-among-bjps-first-list-of-41-candidates-for-rajasthan-polls-4464335%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F7-mps-among-bjps-first-list-of-41-candidates-for-rajasthan-polls-4464335%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F7-mps-among-bjps-first-list-of-41-candidates-for-rajasthan-polls-4464335%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Shares%20Pics%20Showing%20Evidence%20Of%20War%20Crimes%20By%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dramatic%20assault%20launched%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20enclave%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Hamas%20militants%20on%20Saturday%20stormed%20into%20Israeli%20towns%2C%20killing%20more%20than%20600%20Israelis%20and%20escaping%20with%20dozens%20of%20hostages%2C%20in%20the%20deadliest%20day%20for%20Israel%20since%20the%201973%20war.%C2%A0Israel%20responded%20with%20airstrikes%20on%20Gaza%2C%20and%20the%20conflict%20has%20since%20escalated.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20hostages%20are%20now%20being%20held%C2%A0in%20locations%20across%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20horrifying%20pictures%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-video-israeli-couple-2-children-held-hostage-daughter-executed-4461225%23lnitir3rwikpg47bz7i%5C%22%3Evideos%20have%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0showing%C2%A0Hamas%C2%A0fighters%20dragging%20Israeli%20soldiers%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fharrowing-video-shows-woman-being-kidnapped-from-music-festival-by-hamas-terrorists-4460986%5C%22%3E%20civilians%20through%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20streets%20of%20Gaza.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20Hamas%20itself%20shared%20a%20video%20showing%20its%20fighters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palastine-war-hamas-releases-video-of-troops-capturing-3-men-in-israel-4459195%23lnitmw8lqdpe0ca7kv%5C%22%3Ecapturing%20three%20men%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20dressed%20in%20civilian%20clothes.%20Other%20graphic%20visuals%20online%20show%20injured%20Israeli%20soldiers%20and%20civilians%2C%20with%20their%20hands%20tied%2C%20being%20taken%20by%20force%20in%20Hamas%20vehicles.%20In%20one%20video%2C%20the%20Hamas%20group%20is%20seen%20kicking%20and%20hitting%20the%20corpse%20of%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20truck.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20the%20footage%20can%20be%20independently%20verified.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20legal%20and%20security%20experts%20in%20the%20country%20said%20the%20group's%20actions%20constitute%20war%20crimes%2C%20and%20likely%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20since%20the%20assault%20against%20civilians%20was%20so%20broad%20and%20deliberate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20shared%20pictures%20on%20X%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20incriminating%20evidence%20of%20the%20war%20crimes%20committed%20by%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20organization.%26quot%3B%20The%20pictures%20claim%20that%20Hamas%20is%C2%A0killing%20and%20abducting%20civilians%2C%20firing%20missiles%20at%20Israel%2C%20mutilating%20corpses%2C%20using%20civilians%20as%20human%20shields%2C%20and%20concealing%20terrorist%20infrastructure%20in%20civilian%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20incriminating%20evidence%20of%20the%20war%20crimes%20committed%20by%20the%20Hamas%20terrorist%20organization.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgM9mWZVkeG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgM9mWZVkeG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(%40IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIDF%2Fstatus%2F1711210451403501672%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%209%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20official%20account%20of%20Israel%20War%20Room%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20organisation%2C%20also%20shared%20pictures%20of%20women%20and%20men%20kidnapped%20by%20Hamas%20amid%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20did%20not%20say%20how%20many%20hostages%20were%20seized%2C%20but%20the%20number%20of%20Israeli%20nationals%20held%20captive%20by%20Hamas%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented''%2C%20IDF%20spokesman%20Lt.%20Col.%20Jonathan%20Conricus%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3ECNN.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20extremely%20disturbing%20scenes%20for%20any%20Israeli%20to%20see.%20I%20don't%20even%20want%20to%20imagine%20what%20the%20fate%20of%20this%20Israeli%20person%20will%20be%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20these%20blood-thirsty%20animals%2C''%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20Hamas%20spokesman%20claimed%20that%20the%20number%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20taken%20is%20''many%20times%20greater%20than%20what%20Netanyahu%20thinks.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHamas%20has%20committed%20a%20long%20list%20of%20crimes%20in%20this%20attack%20for%20which%20have%20been%20documented%2C%20including%20the%20killing%20of%20civilians%2C%20taking%20civilians%20captive%2C%20and%20abusing%20the%20bodies%20of%20civilians%20and%20soldiers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prof.%20Yuval%20Shany%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20international%20law%20and%20a%20lecturer%20at%20The%20Hebrew%20University%20of%20Jerusalem%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Ffootage-of-hamas-assault-on-civilians-shows-likely-war-crimes-experts-say%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20Of%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696853760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fhv30k6d8_hostages-taken-by-hamas_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-defense-forces-shares-pics-showing-evidence-of-war-crimes-by-hamas-4464457%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20pictures%20and%20videos%20have%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20showing%20Hamas%20fighters%20dragging%20Israeli%20soldiers%20and%20civilians%20through%20the%20street