A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F31171341%2F10.02.2023_-_Reuni%25C3%25A3o_com_o_Presidente_dos_Estados_Unidos_da_Am%25C3%25A9rica_Joe_Biden_52681638789.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBrazil%20is%20a%20big%20country%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%20214%20million.%20It%20is%20the%20second%20most%20populated%20country%20in%20the%20Americas%20and%20third%20in%20land%20area.%20During%20President%20Lula%20da%20Silva%E2%80%99s%20first%20two%20tenures%20from%202002%20to%202010%2C%20millions%20emerged%20from%20poverty%20through%20welfare%20and%20education%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2077%2C%20a%20survivor%20of%20jail%20(2018-20)%20and%20cancer%2C%20Lula%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20poor%20rural%20household.%20He%20was%20the%20seventh%20child%20out%20of%20eight%20children.%20A%20former%20metal%20worker%2C%20he%20rose%20through%20union%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20married%20thrice%3B%20his%20present%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20his%20Workers%20Party%20(PT)%20colleague%2C%20is%2021%20years%20younger.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELula%20was%20elected%20president%20in%20his%20fourth%20attempt%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20person%20from%20outside%20the%20political%20and%20economic%20%C3%A9lite%20who%20did%20not%20have%20a%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20immensely%20popular%20with%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20least%20educated%20section%20of%20the%20society%20because%20of%20cash-transfer%20policies%2C%20backed%20by%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20By%202010%2C%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20population%20was%20benefiting%20from%20such%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20policies%20deepened%20human%20rights%20and%20decreased%20hunger%2C%20poverty%2C%20inequality%2C%20and%20child%20labour.%20Upward%20social%20mobility%20was%20achieved%20through%20access%20to%20education%2C%20including%20the%20use%20of%20quotas%2C%20scholarships%2C%20incentives%2C%20and%20finance.%20By%202017%2C%20nearly%2010%25%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98coloured%E2%80%99%20people%2C%20who%20are%2056%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20graduated%2C%20while%2022%25%20of%20white%20individuals%20also%20graduated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrazil%20became%20a%20recognised%20player%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20was%20a%20leader%20in%20controlling%20climate%20change.%20However%2C%20the%20need%20for%20coalition%20governments%20in%20Brazil%20has%20been%20a%20consistent%20factor.%20Since%20he%20came%20to%20power%2C%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20were%20made%20against%20Lula.%20It%20was%20alleged%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-brazil-lula-corruption-idUSBRE8BA0NH20121211%5C%22%3Ehe%20bought%20votes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20narrow%20win%20as%20president%20last%20year%20showed%20that%20the%20taint%20of%20corruption%20still%20persists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELula%20was%20followed%20by%20his%20chosen%20successor%2C%20Dilma%20Rousseff%2C%20who%20held%20the%20position%20from%202011%20to%202016.%20However%2C%20the%20economic%20situation%20changed%20for%20the%20worse%2C%20as%20demand%20for%20Brazilian%20exports%20fell%2C%20and%20she%20mismanaged%20the%20administration.%20Poverty%20levels%20surged%2C%20public%20services%20deteriorated%2C%20her%20approval%20rating%20plummeted%20to%20less%20than%2030%25%2C%20and%20corruption%20scandals%20contributed%20to%20her%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELula%E2%80%99s%20policies%20were%20further%20discarded%20by%20Michel%20Temer%2C%20who%20succeeded%20Rousseff%2C%20but%20the%20greatest%20change%20came%20with%20President%20Jair%20Bolsonaro%2C%20who%20held%20the%20position%20from%202018%20to%202022.%20He%20is%20known%20for%20his%20extreme%20populist%20nationalism%2C%20which%20ended%20on%20January%208%2C%202023%2C%20when%2C%20in%20protest%20against%20Lula%E2%80%99s%20victory%2C%20his%20supporters%2C%20along%20with%20the%20army%20and%20security%20agencies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D%26ved%3D2ahUKEwiqnvuhyOiBAxXJglYBHYdrAR0QFnoECBEQAQ%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nytimes.com%252Flive%252F2023%252F01%252F09%252Fworld%252Fbrazil-congress-riots-bolsonaro%26usg%3DAOvVaw1o6xThjrB-aZpmPTsvuAx6%26opi%3D89978449%5C%22%3Einvaded%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20main%20governmental%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09154134%2Fimage-1375.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09154134%2Fimage-1375.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09154134%2Fimage-1375-300x136.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09154134%2Fimage-1375-1024x464.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679095%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22544%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Unsplash%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ensuing%20domestic%20and%20international%20denunciation%20of%20the%20riots%20helped%20Lula%2C%20however%2C%20the%20obstacles%20he%20faces%20in%20his%20third%20term%20are%20formidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBolsonaro%E2%80%99s%20term%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBolsonaro%20was%20a%20seven-term%20Congressman%20who%20switched%20parties%20seven%20times.%20He%20%E2%80%9Chad%20no%20friends%20in%20Latin%20America%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20reversed%20Lula%E2%80%99s%20policies%2C%20prioritising%20alliance%20with%20Christian%20nations%20and%20close%20ties%20with%20the%20US.%20He%20was%20undone%20by%20an%20administration%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cobscurantist%2C%20exclusivist%20and%20retrograde%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20popularity%20of%20Lula%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fjair-bolsonaro-brazil-coronavirus-vaccine-anxiety%5C%22%3Einept%20handling%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20since%20he%20was%20a%20vaccine%20denier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHealth%20and%20education%20were%20underfunded%2C%20concerns%20about%20climate%20change%20and%20environment%20grew%2C%20and%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20incumbent%20failed%20to%20get%20re-elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBolsonaro%20traded%20on%20anti-PT%2C%20anti-corruption%2C%20and%20anti-criminal%20sentiment%3B%20he%20thought%20higher%20education%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Ccaptured%20by%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20Left%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20cut%20education%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncome%20growth%20mostly%20went%20to%20the%20better-off.%20In%202021%2C%20there%20were%2033%20million%20people%20living%20in%20poverty%2C%2018%20million%20people%20were%20extremely%20poor%2C%20and%20food%20insecurity%20affected%2015%25%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMechanisms%20that%20explained%20the%20mitigation%20of%20hunger%20were%20dismantled%2C%E2%80%9D%208%2C000%20Cuban%20doctors%20were%20forced%20to%20withdraw%20from%20their%20profession.%20Human%20rights%20concerns%20were%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBolsonaro%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbolsonaro-should-be-tried-crimes-against-humanity-indigenous-leaders-say-n1272193%5C%22%3Eregarded%3C%2Fa%3E%20indigenous%20rights%20as%20%E2%80%9Cobstacles%E2%80%9D%20to%20agri-business%2C%20illegal%20timber%20and%20mining%2C%20and%20was%20prepared%20to%20use%20violence%20to%20achieve%20his%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2F20191121-god-family-homeland-brazil-s-bolsonaro-launches-new-party%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20NGOs%20%E2%80%9Canti-family%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Canti-god%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Canti-nation%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-life%E2%80%9D%20(abortion).%20He%20recognised%20the%20power%20of%20the%20military%20and%20police%20families%20who%20supported%20the%20use%20of%20violence%20to%20combat%20crime%2C%20and%20favoured%20gun%20ownership%2C%20brutal%20policing%20and%20police%20autonomy.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-brazil-environment-idUSKBN22J256%5C%22%3Ebrought%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20military%20officers%20into%20government%20positions%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Ca%20certain%20nostalgia%20for%20the%20military%20dictatorships%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20deployed%20social%20media%20for%20%E2%80%9Cnon-stop%20confrontation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20electoral%20defeat%20evoked%20international%20relief%20due%20to%20his%20reputation%20as%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F01%2F09%2Fopinion%2Fbrazil-protests-bolsonaro.html%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Trump%20of%20the%20Tropics%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Lula%20faces%20a%20difficult%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20need%20to%20regain%20political%20and%20personal%20credibility%20for%20Lula%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20secured%20only%20a%20slim%20majority%20of%2051-49%25%2C%20Bolsonaro%20loyalists%20control%20half%20of%20the%2026%20states%2C%20the%20federal%20capital%2C%20and%20the%20three%20most%20populated%20and%20developed%20states.%20The%20legislature%20and%20courts%20are%20empowered%20and%20combative.%20There%20are%20fissures%20along%20race%2C%20income%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20religious%20lines.%20Pro%20and%20anti-Lula%20voters%20%E2%80%9Cdisagreed%20on%20basically%20everything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20deeply%20polarised%20Brazil%2C%20Lula%20will%20have%20to%20regain%20political%20and%20personal%20credibility%2C%20deal%20with%20rightist%20and%20centre-right%20governors%2C%20the%20Senate%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20military%20with%20suspect%20loyalty%2C%20a%20stagnant%20economy%2C%20fiscal%20deficit%2C%20and%20about%20one-third%2C%20or%2060-70%20million%20people%2C%20in%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20%E2%80%9Call%20eyes%20are%20on%20Brazil%20and%20hopes%20are%20high.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELula%20will%20be%20a%20one-term%20president%20and%20this%20is%20his%20%E2%80%9Clast%20chance%2C%20and%20he%20has%20no%20room%20for%20error.%E2%80%9D%20While%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20intimidated%20in%20contact%20with%20powerful%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20%E2%80%9Cquintessential%20political%20negotiator%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20relations%20with%20the%20establishment%20were%20never%20easy%2C%20though%20he%20was%20more%20pragmatic%20and%20popular%20than%20the%20PT.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELula%20will%20enjoy%20strong%20support%20from%20feminists%20and%20indigenous%20people%20when%20he%20focusses%20on%20sustainable%20growth%2C%20eradication%20of%20poverty%2C%20and%20extension%20of%20social%20programmes%20for%20the%20extreme%20poor%20and%20women.%20He%20must%20re-establish%20state%20control%20and%20restore%20public%20security%20as%20a%20social%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELula%20has%20chosen%20a%20conservative%20vice-president%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Crelies%20on%20fewer%20people%20and%20takes%20almost%20all%20his%20important%20decisions%20alone.%E2%80%9D%20His%20cabinet%20is%20oversized%20with%20the%20Left%20under-represented%2C%20and%20three%20centrist%20parties%20are%20key%20to%20his%20success%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20defections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20opinions%20of%20the%20police%20and%20the%20army%20will%20be%20important.%20With%2086%20different%20police%20forces%2C%20and%20numerous%20veto%20holders%2C%20making%20reforms%20in%20reducing%20racial%20inequality%20in%20the%20police%2C%20authoritarian%20community%20policing%20and%20excessive%20violence%20will%20be%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20Brazil%20is%20technologically%20advanced%20and%20is%20doing%20well%20in%20the%20financial%20services%20sector%2C%20natural%20resources%20still%20remain%20key%20to%20its%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELula%20encounters%20environmental%20issues%20related%20to%20dams%2C%20highways%2C%20gas%2C%20oil%2C%20biofue