%20of%20female%20camaraderie%20and%20adventure.%20The%20film%20follows%20a%20group%20of%20ordinary%20women%20who%20transform%20into%20bikers%20and%20embark%20on%20a%20life-changing%20journey%20to%20the%20highest%20motorable%20pass%20in%20the%20world.%20Directed%20by%20Tarun%20Dudeja%2C%20%26quot%3BDhak%20Dhak%26quot%3B%20aims%20to%20entertain%20while%20delivering%20a%20meaningful%20message%20about%20freedom%20and%20female%20empowerment.%20The%20film%20is%20set%20to%20release%20on%20October%2013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftaapsee-pannu-presents-dhak-dhak-trailer-a-riveting-tale-of-female-friendship-and-adventure%2Farticleshow%2F104286549.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B100%25%20With%20Caste%20Census%2C%20Must%20Get%20It%20Done%26quot%3B%3A%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20At%20Congress%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20has%20unanimously%20endorsed%20a%20call%20for%20caste%20census%20at%20a%20meeting%20held%20today.%20The%20party%20alleged%20that%20India%20is%20the%20only%20G20%20nation%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20conduct%20such%20a%20census%2C%20declaring%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bmatter%20of%20shame%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%26quot%3Bcheating%26quot%3B%20the%20country's%20deprived%20sections%20by%20not%20releasing%20the%20data%20of%20the%202011%20Socio%20Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20and%20not%20carrying%20out%20a%20fresh%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(the%20government)%20has%20also%20failed%20in%20its%20Constitutional%20duty%20by%20inordinately%20postponing%20the%20decadal%20Census%20that%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20conducted%20in%202021%20or%20soon%20thereafter%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20Working%20Committee%2C%20the%20party's%20highest%20decision-making%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20initiative%20was%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20in%20an%20address%20later%2C%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20%26quot%3Bput%20pressure%20on%20the%20BJP%20to%20conduct%20this%26quot%3B.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bshying%20away%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20conduction%20of%20a%20caste%20census%20does%20not%20depend%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20political%20decision.%20This%20is%20a%20decision%20for%20providing%20justice%20to%20the%20downtrodden...%20Litmus%20tests%20work%20in%20chemistry%2C%20not%20in%20politics.%20We%20are%20promising%20caste%20census%20because%20we%20sincerely%20believe%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20one%20hundred%20per%20cent%20with%20the%20caste%20census%20and%20we%20must%20get%20it%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20party%20till%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20successor%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20said%20the%20party%20has%20consistently%20raised%20its%20demand%20for%20a%20nationwide%20caste-based%20census.%20The%20demand%20has%20gained%20widespread%20public%20support%20especially%20after%20the%20Bihar%20Government's%20release%20of%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20proper%20implementation%20and%20delivery%20of%20government%20programmes%20and%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20we%20have%20scientific%20socio-economic%20data%20of%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20including%20their%20numbers%2C%20representation%2C%20and%20economic%20and%20social%20condition.%20Thus%2C%20it%20becomes%20important%20that%20we%20must%20deliberate%20upon%20the%20issue%20of%20Caste-based%20Census%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20decision%20came%20as%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20the%20dates%20for%20election%20in%20five%20states.%20Three%20of%20them%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20lie%20in%20the%20heartland%20where%20caste-based%20politics%20dominates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20which%20cautiously%20held%20back%20the%202011%20caste%20report%2C%20has%20been%C2%A0%20vocal%20over%20a%20census%20over%20the%20last%20months%2C%20declaring%20it%20is%20the%20way%20forward%20to%20a%20proper%20and%20equitable%20social%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20had%20written%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20seeking%20implementation%20of%20a%20caste%20census.%20Having%20proper%20caste-wise%20data%20will%20help%20governments%20implement%20welfare%20and%20social%20security%20schemes%20better%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696851660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fp7hcct3g_rahul-gandhi-mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_16_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-makes-it-official-throws-weight-behind-caste-census-demand-4464130%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20has%20unanimously%20endorsed%20a%20call%20for%20caste%20census%20at%20a%20meeting%20held%20today.%20Sources%20said%20the%20initiative%20was%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20later%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20%26quot%3Bput%20pressure%20on%20the%20BJP%20to%20conduct%20this%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-makes-it-official-throws-weight-behind-caste-census-demand-4464130%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-makes-it-official-throws-weight-behind-caste-census-demand-4464130%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-makes-it-official-throws-weight-behind-caste-census-demand-4464130%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delta%20cu