it.%20The%20available%20refunds%20plus%20interest%20total%20%2427.3%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20covers%20US%20citizens%20who%20had%20purchased%20non-refundable%20tickets%20for%20Delta%20flights%20scheduled%20to%20depart%20between%20March%201%2C%202020%20and%20April%2030%2C%202021.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F06%2Fbusiness%2Fdelta-covid-flight-cancellation-settlement%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%2014%2C000%20members%20of%20the%20class%20had%20submitted%20their%20claims%20by%20the%20September%2015%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20breached%20its%20contractual%20obligation%20to%20issue%20refunds%20for%20the%20canceled%20flights%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20claimed.%20It%20also%20understaffed%20its%20call%20centers%20and%20made%20it%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%26quot%3B%20to%20request%20refunds%20online%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fairlineticketsettlement.com%2FContent%2FDocuments%2FSettlement%2520Agreement.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edraft%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20settlement%20agreement%2C%20Delta%20said%20that%20it%20denied%20%26quot%3Beach%20and%20every%20allegation%20of%20liability%2C%20wrongdoing%2C%20and%20damage%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20it%20was%20settling%20the%20lawsuit%20%26quot%3Bto%20avoid%20the%20substantial%20expense%2C%20inconvenience%2C%20burden%2C%20and%20disruption%20of%20continued%20litigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Eleanor%20L.%20Ross%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fairlineticketsettlement.com%2FContent%2FDocuments%2FFinal%2520Approval%2520Order.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapproved%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20settlement%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20will%20also%20pay%20attorneys'%20fees%20totalling%20%242.285%20million%20for%20the%20class%20members%2C%20an%20estimated%20%24246%2C465%20for%20settlement%20administration%20costs%2C%20%2451