uot%3Bwe%20will%20need%20the%20support%20of%20our%20friends%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20when%20heart-bleeding%20so-called%20liberals%20come%20and%20say%20we%20have%20to%20stop%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Israeli%20government's%20resettlement%20efforts%20contributed%20to%20the%20tension%20in%20the%20region%2C%20Lapid%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20only%20reason%20they%20attacked%20women%2C%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%20is%20because%20they%20can%20do%20it%20and%20they%20want%20to%20kill%20Jews.%20I%20am%20the%20son%20of%20a%20Holocaust%20survivor.%20We%20know%20anti-Semitism%20when%20we%20see%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELapid%20conceded%20the%20intelligence%20failure%20to%20prevent%20an%20attack%20of%20this%20scale.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20huge%20intelligence%20failure%20on%20our%20hands%20and%20we%20will%20deal%20with%20it%20after%20we%20deal%20with%20the%20more%20urgent%20thing%20of%20making%20sure%20that%20we%20take%20their%20capabilities.%20This%20was%20a%20surprise%20attack%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20of%20hiding%20from%20it.%20But%20we%20have%20a%20good%20history%20of%20learning%20from%20mistakes%20instead%20of%20agonising%20over%20them.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20leader%20said%20the%20country%20needs%20the%20support%20of%20the%20global%20community%20now.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20tend%20to%20forget%20that%20we%20left%20Gaza%2020%20years%20back%20and%20told%20them%20to%20build%20a%20life%20for%20themselves.%20But%20they%20built%20training%20camps%20for%20Hamas%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20and%20fired%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20rockets%20at%20Israel.%20Right%20now%2C%20we%20need%20the%20global%20community's%20support%20and%20patience.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20deal%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696849140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fe8h8ksk_ex-israel-pm-ndtv-split-65