20spent%20his%20final%20moments%20surrounded%20by%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20who%20respectfully%20asked%20for%20privacy%20during%20this%20immensely%20sad%20and%20difficult%20period.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20ex-wife%2C%20Eileen%20Gordon%2C%20and%20their%20four%20children%20Aidan%2C%20Margaux%2C%20Felicia%2C%20and%20Giana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20his%20family%20said%2C%20''We%20deeply%20mourn%20the%20loss%20of%20our%20beloved%20patriarch%20Michael.%20His%20culinary%20brilliance%2C%20boundless%20creativity%2C%20and%20unwavering%20commitment%20to%20family%20were%20at%20the%20core%20of%20his%20being.%20He%20brought%20people%20together%20through%20the%20joy%20of%20shared%20meals%2C%20fostering%20lasting%20memories%20around%20the%20table.%20As%20we%20navigate%20this%20profound%20loss%2C%20we%20hold%20dear%20the%20moments%20we%20cherished%20with%20him%2C%20both%20in%20his%20kitchens%20and%20in%20our%20hearts.%20His%20legacy%20will%20forever%20live%20on%20in%20the%20love%20he%20poured%20into%20every%20dish%20and%20the%20passion%20he%20instilled%20in%20all%20of%20us%20to%20savor%20life's%20flavors.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Flife-style%2Fmichael-chiarello-death-cause-allergic-reaction-b2426424.html%23lniqxzqrht9bdmxqi4s%5C%22%3EIndependent%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20was%20born%20on%20January%2026%2C%201962%2C%20and%20graduated%20from%20the%20Culinary%20Institute%20of%20America%20in%20New%20York%20at%20the%20age%20of%2020.%20In%201985%2C%20he%20was%20recognised%20as%20Chef%20of%20the%20Year%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3EFood%20%26amp%3B%20Wine%20Magazine.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0He%20hosted%20shows%20on%20PBS%2C%20Food%20Network%2C%20Fine%20Living%2C%20and%20Cooking%20Channel%20for%20a%20decade%20and%20appeared%20on%20%3Cem%3ETop%20Chef%2C%20Top%20Chef%20Masters%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20The%20Next%20Iron%20Chef.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201987%2C%20he%20opened%20his%20critically%20acclaimed%20restaurant%20Tra%20Vigne%20in%20Napa%20Valley%2C%20California%2C%20before%20opening%20other%20restaurants%20such%20as%20Bottega%2C%20Coqueta%2C%20and%20Ottimo.%C2%A0He%20also%20ventured%20into%20winemaking%20in%201999%2C%20creating%20Chiarello%20Family%20Vineyards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chiarello%20received%20a%20Daytime%20Emmy%20in%202005%20for%20Outstanding%20Service%20Show%20Host%20for%20his%20Food%20Network%20show%20%E2%80%98Easy%20Entertaining%20with%20Michael%20Chiarello.'%20Apart%20from%20his%20TV%20career%2C%20he%20also%20wrote%20several%20books%2C%20including%20Bottega%3A%20Bold%20Italian%20Flavors%20from%20the%20Heart%20of%20California's%20Wine%20Country%2C%20At%20Home%20with%20Michael%20Chiarello%3A%20Easy%20Entertaining%2C%20and%20Michael%20Chiarello's%20Casual%20Cooking.%C2%A0He%20has%20also%20been%20praised%20for%20a%20culinary%20philosophy%20that%20revolved%20around%20sustainability%20and%20a%20culture%20of%20shared%20meals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696848840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fl8qe9mtg_michael-chiarello_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcelebrity-chef-michael-chiarello-dies-at-61-after-going-into-anaphylactic-shock-4464204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20died%20at%20Queen%20of%20the%20Valley%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Napa%2C%20California%20where%20he%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20an%20acute%20allergic%20reaction%20that%20led%20to%20anaphylactic%20shock.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcelebrity-chef-michael-chiarello-dies-at-61-after-going-into-anaphylactic-shock-4464204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcelebrity-chef-michael-chiarello-dies-at-61-after-going-into-anaphylactic-shock-4464204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw