2https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09151742%2FF4mlUrzbMAEdaNo.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20letter%20by%20eight%20senior%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20in%20Manipur%20to%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20has%20pointed%20to%20the%20anger%20against%20the%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20amidst%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20and%20also%20expressed%20confusion%20over%20whether%20Article%20355%20is%20imposed%20in%20the%20state%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Flooking-northeast-manipur-bjp-leaders-doubt-article-355-8973283%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20writers%20of%20the%20letter%20are%20state%20BJP%20president%20A.%20Sharda%20Devi%2C%20whose%20house%2C%20the%20report%20notes%20has%20been%20targeted%20%E2%80%9Csix%20times%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20violence%20which%20began%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPublic%20anger%20and%20protest%20is%20now%20slowly%20turning%20the%20tide%2C%20putting%20the%20sole%20onus%20of%20prolonged%20disturbances%20%5Bon%5D%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20leaders%20wrote%2C%20according%20to%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20pushed%20for%20Article%20355%20to%20be%20revoked%2C%20but%20not%20before%20adding%20an%20important%20caveat%3A%20%E2%80%9CArticle%20355%20%3Cem%3Eif%20there%20is%20anything%20as%20such%20imposed%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20The%20emphasis%20is%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20pressed%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20command%20of%20the%20Unified%20Command%E2%80%9D%20be%20restored%20to%20CM%20Biren%20so%20that%20it%20can%20win%20back%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArticle%20355%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20shall%20be%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20Union%20to%20protect%20every%20State%20against%20external%20aggression%20and%20internal%20disturbance%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20of%20every%20State%20is%20carried%20on%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20this%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArticle%20356%20promises%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20demand%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20residents%20ever%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20Article%20355%20that%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20mystery%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-centre-says-no-information-on-article-355%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20early%20August%20this%20year%20that%20in%20response%20to%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20query%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%20had%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20categorically%20stated%20that%20it%20had%20no%20information%20on%20any%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20Centre%20under%20Article%20355%20of%20the%20Constitution%20between%20January%202023%20and%20June%2013%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20early%20as%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-mysterious-case-of-the-imposition-of-article-355-in-manipur%5C%22%3Ein%20a%20press%20conference%20the%20then%20head%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20state%20police%2C%20DGP%20P%20Doungel%2C%20had%20said%20Article%20355%20had%20been%20imposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20assigned%20a%20security%20advisor%20to%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERetired%20IPS%20officer%20and%20former%20CRPF%20DG%20Kuldiep%20Singh%20is%20still%20security%20advisor%20and%20heads%20the%20unified%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696848349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fup