iss%20match%20against%20Afghanistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696846510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104283510%2Cimgsize-45228.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fodi-world-cup-shubman-gill-to-miss-match-against-afghanistan%2Farticleshow%2F104283493.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20already%20missed%20the%20opening%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20Australia%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Sunday%20due%20to%20dengue%20fever%2C%20India's%20opener%20Subhman%20Gill%20will%20remain%20unavailable%20for%20the%20team's%20next%20game%20against%20Afghanistan%2C%20confirmed%20BCCI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NewsClick%20Case%3A%20Do%20Allegations%20Justify%20Invoking%20of%20UAPA%3F%20Legal%20Experts%20Weigh%20In.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F16195602%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-16-at-7.55.39-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20its%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakraborty%20face%20charges%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20in%20a%20case%20registered%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Cell%2C%20legal%20experts%20say%20that%20the%20use%20of%20the%20anti-terror%20law%20is%20grossly%20disproportionate%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20make%20out%20a%20terror%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPurkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20were%20held%20on%20October%203%20after%20daylong%20questioning%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police.%20On%20the%20same%20day%2C%20nearly%2046%20journalists%2C%20commentators%20and%20other%20staff%20with%20links%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20raided%2C%20questioned%20and%20had%20their%20devices%20seized.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20action%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20being%20described%20as%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20attacks%20on%20media%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20senior%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20advocate%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Sanjay%20Hegde%20said%20that%20the%20UAPA%20charge%20against%20Purkayastha%20is%20not%20justified.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20UAPA%20(charge)%20is%20certainly%20not%20justified.%20It%20is%20grossly%20disproportionate%20and%20it%20is%20intended%20to%20terrorise%20normal%20journalism.%20Money%20has%20not%20only%20been%20received%20(by%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E)%20through%20normal%20public%20channels%20but%20as%20a%20business%20transaction.%20There%20is%20no%20proven%20quid%20pro%20quo%20for%20running%20any%20kind%20of%20story.%20Even%20if%20there%20was%20a%20quid%20pro%20quo%20for%20running%20any%20kind%20of%20story%2C%20that%20too%20is%20not%20covered%20by%20criminal%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20people%20accept%20advertorials%20too%20and%20that%20is%20not%20normally%20covered%20by%20criminal%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20police%20in%20its%20FIR%20filed%20on%20August%2017%2C%202023%20invoked%20multiple%20sections%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20amount%E2%80%9D%20of%20Chinese%20funding%20was%20used%20to%20publish%20%E2%80%9Cpaid%20news%E2%80%9D%20which%20criticised%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20promoted%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Chinese%2C%20though%20the%20FIR%20does%20not%20provide%20any%20details%20of%20these%20alleged%20paid%20news%20items.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20alleges%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20criminal%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20involving%20the%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20infusion%20of%20funds%E2%80%9D%20by%20Chinese%20companies%20Xiaomi%20and%20Vivo%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cspirited%20defence%20of%20legal%20cases%E2%80%9D%20against%20these%20telecom%20firms%20by%20%E2%80%9CGautam%20Bhatia%E2%80%9D%20who%20is%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20person%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20importantly%20China%20is%20not%20an%20enemy%20state%2C%20we%20are%20not%20at%20war%20with%20China-there%20has%20been%20no%20such%20declaration.%20There%20is%20no%20criminal%20case%20for%20Purkayastha%20to%20answer%2C%20much%20less%20a%20UAPA%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hegde.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Madan%20B.%20Lokur%20said%20that%20while%20journalists%20are%20not%20outside%20the%20purview%20of%20UAPA%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20evidence%20to%20invoke%20the%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20whatever%20material%20is%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20make%20out%20a%20case%20under%20UAPA.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20a%20journalist%20is%20outside%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20UAPA%2C%20but%20in%20this%20case%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPurkayastha%20is%20not%20the%20first%20journalist%20to%20face%20UAPA%20charges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2F16-indian-journalists-have-been-charged-under-uapa-7-are-currently-behind-bars%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20Free%20Speech%20Collective%2C%2016%20journalists%20have%20been%20jailed%20and%20charged%20under%20the%20stringent%20anti-terror%20act%20since%202010%2C%20of%20whom%20seven%20are%20currently%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Deepak%20Gupta%20said%20that%20while%20no%20one%20is%20above%20the%20law%2C%20a%20fair%20trial%20should%20be%20conducted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLaw%20cannot%20be%20misused%20to%20persecute%20or%20get%20even%20with%20the%20people%20who%20are%20critical%20of%20the%20government%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20nobody%20is%20above%20the%20law.%20Everybody%20is%20subject%20to%20the%20law%20and%20Mr%20Pukayastha%20has%20to%20face%20the%20law%20but%20he%20should%20get%20a%20fair%20trial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%206%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20%E2%80%93%20while%20denying%20interim%20relief%20to%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20the%20allegations%20are%20such%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20warrant%20the%20grant%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fdelhi-high-court-newsclick-arrest-prabir-purkayastha-delhi-police-remand-uapa-239493%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eimmediate%20relief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enoted%20that%20the%20remand%20application%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20reasons%20for%20arrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20judges%20have%20also%20criticised%20the%20initial%20denial%20of%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20to%20Purkayastha%20and%20the%20failure%20to%20disclose%20the%20grounds%20for%20arrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20duo%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Ffir-given-only-yesterday-allegations-untenable-and-bogus-newsclick%5C%22%3Egiven%20a%20copy%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20FIR%20only%20after%20a%20Delhi%20court%20granted%20their%20plea%2C%20which%20was%20opposed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%20NewsClick%20described%20the%20charges%20in%20the%20FIR%20as%20%E2%80%9Cex%20facie%20untenable%20and%20bogus%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPursuant%20to%20directions%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Special%20Judge%2C%20Patiala%20House%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20was%20supplied%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Special%20Cell%20only%20yesterday%20(Thursday)%20night.%20We%20immediately%20moved%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi%20seeking%20quashing%20of%20the%20FIR%20as%20well%20as%20release%20of%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20Amit%20Chakraborty%20from%20their%20illegal%20police%20custody.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELokur%20said%20that%20the%20denial%20of%20the%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20was%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20wrong.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20person%20who%20is%20arrested%20is%20entitled%20to%20have%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20against%20him%20and%20the%20grounds%20of%20arrest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%2C%20Purkayastha%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20Kapil%20Sibal%20said%20on%20October%206%20that%20the%20accused%20received%20the%20FIR%20on%20October%205%2C%20and%20that%20the%20remand%20order%20did%20not%20include%20the%20grounds%20of%20arrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20delivered%20on%20October%203%20in%20a%20separate%20money%20laundering%20case%20in%20which%20it%20said%20that%20the%20ED%20should%20be%20transparent%20and%20above%20board%20in%20functioning%2C%20and%20held%20that%20the%20agency%20should%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-ed-transparency-vindictive%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efurnish%20the%20grounds%20for%20arrest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20accused%20in%20writing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESibal%20reiterated%20in%20his%20arguments%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20grounds%20had%20not%20been%20given%2C%20as%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20the%20centre%20is%20planning%20to%20file%20a%20review%20against%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20October%203%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C..They%20say%20the%20grounds%20are%20in%20the%20arrest%20memo.%20I%20have%20shown%20you%20the%20arrest%20memo%2C%20the%20grounds%20are%20not%20there.%20The%20fact%20that%20a%20review%20is%20being%20filed%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20change%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbarandbench%2Fstatus%2F1711275635061174760%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20high%20court%20reserved%20its%20order%20on%20Monday%20on%20the%20plea%20by%20Purkayastha%20and%20Chakraborty%20challenging%20their%20arrest%2C%20remand%20and%20the%20FIR%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696846506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F08%2F16195602%2FScreen-Shot-2021-08-16-at-7.55.39-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-case-allegations-uapa-legal-experts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NewsClick%20founder%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20its%20HR%20head%20Amit%20Chakraborty%20were%20held%20on%20October%203.%20The%20Delhi%20police%20claim%20the%20news%20portal%20received%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20amount%E2%80%9D%20of%20Chinese%