r-israeli-victims-at-un-human-rights-council%2Farticleshow%2F104282620.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-leads-moment-of-silence-for-israeli-victims-at-un-human-rights-council%2Famp_articleshow%2F104282620.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-leads-moment-of-silence-for-israeli-victims-at-un-human-rights-council%2Famp_articleshow%2F104282620.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Is%20the%20Now%20Banned%20JKDFP%20and%20Who%20Is%20its%20Leader%20Shabir%20Shah%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09145657%2F9745167b-3b0b-45ec-8e90-b2a463a41565.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20decision%20to%20ban%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Democratic%20Freedom%20Party%20(JKDFP)%2C%20a%20separatist%20outfit%20led%20by%20the%20incarcerated%20Hurriyat%20leader%20Shabir%20Shah%2C%20marks%20another%20chapter%20in%20a%20process%20set%20in%20motion%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%202019%20to%20curtail%20separatist%20politics%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notification%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20said%20that%20the%20outfit%20has%20links%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20it%20was%20involved%20in%20fund%20raising%20for%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%20and%E2%80%A6%20terrorist%20activities%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20are%20prejudicial%20to%20the%20integrity%2C%20sovereignty%2C%20security%20and%20communal%20harmony%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20and%20prompt%20action%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20outfit%2C%20the%20notification%20states%20that%20the%20party%20has%20alleged%20links%20with%20%E2%80%9Cbanned%20terrorist%20organisations%E2%80%9D%20and%20it%20wants%20to%20create%20%E2%80%9Ca%20separate%20Islamic%20State%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJKDFP%20and%20its%20members%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20violent%20terrorist%20activities%20..%2C%20thereby%20endangering%20the%20security%20and%20public%20order%20of%20the%20State%2C%20and%20its%20anti-national%20activities%20also%20show%20disrespect%20and%20disregard%20to%20the%20constitutional%20authority%20and%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20notification%20said%2C%20declaring%20the%20outfit%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunlawful%20association%E2%80%9D%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA)%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrackdown%20on%20JKDFP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJKDFP%20is%20the%20fourth%20separatist%20outfit%20to%20face%20the%20ban%20under%20the%20UAPA%20after%20Jammu%20Kashmir%20Liberation%20Front%20(JKLF)%2C%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20and%20Dukhtaran-e-Millat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crackdown%20on%20JKDFP%20started%20in%202017%20when%20Shabir%20Shah%2C%20its%20president%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20a%202005%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20initially%20investigated%20by%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Cell%20following%20the%20arrest%20of%20Mohammad%20Aslam%20Wani%2C%20a%20Kashmiri%20resident%20who%20reportedly%20claimed%20to%20be%20working%20as%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20conduit%20in%20hawala%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20chargesheet%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20which%20took%20over%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20case%20in%202007%2C%20accused%20Shah%20and%20Wani%20of%20being%20in%20touch%20with%20Hafiz%20Saeed%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Jaish-e-Mohammad%20based%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECracking%20the%20whip%2C%20the%20agency%20seized%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20Srinagar%20residence.%20Another%20property%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20a%20prominent%20Srinagar-based%20doctor%20who%20has%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20money%20laundering%2C%20was%20also%20attached.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Wani%2C%20the%20alleged%20hawala%20conduit%20whose%20statement%20became%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20financial%20investigation%20against%20the%20separatist%20leader%2C%20was%20cleared%20of%20hawala%20charges%20by%20a%20court%20in%202010%2C%20even%20though%20he%20was%20convicted%20for%20illegal%20possession%20of%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESweeping%20crackdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202019%2C%20Shah%20was%20already%20in%20jail%20when%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20arrested%20him%20in%20a%20terror%20funding%20case%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20sweeping%20crackdown%20on%20separatist%20groups%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20mainstream%20leaders%20were%20also%20detained%20ahead%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20downgrading%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20terror%20funding%20case%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20NIA%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20a%20sting%20operation%20by%20a%20Delhi-based%20TV%20network%20which%20caught%20Nayeem%20Khan%2C%20another%20Hurriyat%20leader%2C%20allegedly%20admitting%20to%20receiving%20funds%20for%20financing%20protests%20and%20violence%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%20has%20denied%20the%20sting%20and%20accused%20the%20network%20of%20using%20the%20footage%20%E2%80%9Cout%20of%20context%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJKLF%20chief%20Yasin%20Malik%20and%20other%20Hurriyat%20leaders%20and%20activists%20are%20languishing%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Tihar%20jail%20in%20the%20case.%20Malik%20has%20pleaded%20guilty%20and%20was%20awarded%20a%20life%20term%20for%20waging%20war%20against%20India%20(Section%20121%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code)%20and%20raising%20terror%20funds%20under%20the%20UAPA%20(Section%2017)%2C%20besides%20other%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAltaf%20Shah%20alias%20%E2%80%98Funtoosh%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20middle-rung%20separatist%20leader%20and%20son-in-law%20of%20the%20late%20Hurriyat%20hawk%20Syed%20Ali%20Geelani%2C%20passed%20away%20in%20jail%20awaiting%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20trial%20in%20the%20terror%20funding%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20of%20separatism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShah%20embraced%20politics%20at%20a%20young%20age%20and%20he%20has%20spent%20more%20than%2030%20years%20of%20his%20life%20in%20jail%2C%20earning%20the%20nickname%20of%20%E2%80%98Nelson%20Mandela%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kadipora%20village%20in%201953%2C%20the%20JKDFP%20chief%20was%20reportedly%20first%20arrested%20as%20a%20teenager%20in%201968%2C%20marking%20his%20first%20brush%20with%20politics.%20In%20later%20years%2C%20he%20was%20repeatedly%20caught%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20law%20for%20advocating%20the%20right%20to%20self-determination%20of%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20detentions%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20his%20education%20and%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20complete%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20JKDFP%20chief%20formed%20the%20%E2%80%98Young%20Men%E2%80%99s%20League%E2%80%99%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Kashmiri%20separatist%20outfits%2C%20along%20with%20other%20colleagues%2C%20writes%20Jammu-based%20historian%20and%20academic%20Rekha%20Chowdhary%20in%20her%202019%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%3A%201990%20and%20beyond%3A%20Competitive%20politics%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20separatism%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pakistan%20split%20into%20two%20in%201971%2C%20Shah%20shuttled%20frequently%20between%20jail%20terms%20and%20hideouts%2C%20sometimes%20for%20opposing%20the%20Shimla%20Agreement%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20and%20on%20one%20occasion%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%201975%20accord%20between%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Sheikh%20Abdullah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20controversial%20accord%20has%20been%20blamed%20by%20opponents%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20National%20Conference%20founder%2C%20whose%20career%20rose%20meteorically%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20his%20opposition%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20to%20save%20himself%20from%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20who%20was%20fresh%20from%20inflicting%20a%20crushing%20defeat%20on%20Islamabad%20by%20splitting%20the%20country%20into%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201974%2C%20Shah%20joined%20JKPL%2C%20which%20advocated%20secession%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20a%20government%20officer%2C%20was%20reportedly%20killed%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20while%20his%20brother%20won%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%20in%201987%2C%20the%20irregularities%20in%20which%20are%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20become%20one%20of%20the%20trigger%20for%20insurgency%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20birth%20of%20Hurriyat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20Parties%20Hurriyat%20Conference%20(APHC)%20was%20formed%20on%20July%2031%2C%201993%2C%20clubbing%20together%20all%20the%20separatist%20outfits%20of%20Kashmir.%20JKPL%20was%20one%20of%20the%20seven%20members%20of%20the%20APHC%E2%80%99s%20Executive%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELondon-based%20Amnesty%20International%20declared%20Shah%20a%20%E2%80%98Prisoner%20of%20Conscience%E2%80%99%20in%201993%20for%20his%20long%20run%20in%20jail.%20But%20he%20rubbed%20many%20in%20the%20Hurriyat%20the%20wrong%20way%20for%20consistently%20advocating%20dialogue%20with%20New%20Delhi%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20was%20facing%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20in%20the%20form%20of%20armed%20insurgency%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20went%20against%20the%20Hurriyat%20by%20holding%20parleys%20with%20K.C.%20Pant%2C%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20first%20Kashmir%20interlocutor%2C%20V.P.%20Singh%20and%20the%20US%20Ambassador%20Frank%20Wisner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20when%20the%20APHC%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Maulana%20Abbas%20Ansari%2C%20announced%20its%20intent%20to%20hold%20a%20dialogue%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20Shah%20jumped%20ship%20along%20with%20the%20separatist%20leader%20Syed%20Ali%20Geelani%20and%20JKLF%20chief%20to%20form%20a%20rival%20faction%20of%20the%20Hurriyat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20later%2C%20in%202014%2C%20Shah%2C%20who%20has%20been%20switching%20between%20the%20hardline%20and%20moderate%20factions%20of%20the%20Hurriyat%2C%20caused%20a%20third%20split%20in%20the%20APHC%20by%20launching%20the%20JK%20Hurriyat%20Conference%20after%20being%20reportedly%20miffed%20with%20the%20faction%20of%20the%20Hurriyat%20led%20by%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20on%20JKDFP%20comes%20days%20after%20authorities%20lifted%20curbs%20on%20Mirwaiz%20who%20was%20allegedly%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%20It%20is%20interesting%20that%20it%20took%20the%20Centre%20more%20than%20four%20years%20to%20impose%20the%20ban%20on%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696844723000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09145657%2F9745167b-3b0b-45ec-8e90-b2a463a41565.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fexplained-what-is-the-now-banned-jkdfp-and-who-is-its-leader-shabir-shah%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crackdown%20on%20JKDFP%20started%20in%202017%20when%20Shabir%20Shah%2C%20its%20president%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%202005%20money%20laundering%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fexplained-what-is-the-now-banned-jkdfp-and-who-is-its-leader-shabir-shah%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netflix%20U.K.%E2%80%99s%20Prod