-how-mossad-functions-and-how-it-failed-to-stop-hamas-attack-4463289%5C%22%3EExplained%3A%20How%20Mossad%20Functions%20And%20Why%20It%20Failed%20To%20Stop%20Hamas%20Attack%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2056-year-old%2C%20a%20former%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20soldier%2C%20lives%20around%205%20km%20from%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20Mosque%2C%20the%20third%20holiest%20site%20in%20Islam%20after%20Mecca%20and%20Medina%2C%20located%20on%20the%20Temple%20Mount%2C%20one%20of%20the%20holiest%20sites%20in%20Judaism.%20Mr%20Zakh's%20parents%2C%20both%20in%20their%2080s%2C%20reside%20in%20Be'er%20Sheva%2C%20a%20city%20over%20a%20100%20km%20south%20of%20Jerusalem%20while%20his%20sister%20and%20daughter%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20over%2060%20km%20away%20in%20the%20northwest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20thuds%20of%20falling%20rockets%20rang%20in%20his%20ears%2C%20Mr%20Zakh%2C%20a%20cricket%20aficionado%2C%20and%20fan%20of%20Mumbai's%20fabled%20Iranian%20cafes%2C%20looked%20at%20the%20family%20WhatsApp%20group%20and%20saw%20anxious%20messages%20from%20his%20relatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20internet%20resources%20and%20TV%20we%20came%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20extent%20of%20what%20has%20happened.%20Although%20warning%20signs%20kept%20surfacing%20over%20the%20years%2C%20this%20was%20far%20more%20than%20what%20could%20have%20been%20imagined%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BThe%20IDF%20had%20let%20us%20down%20extremely%20badly.%20Definitely%20a%20shock%20followed%20by%20a%20realisation%20that%20things%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20the%20same%20before%20and%20after%20this%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisrael-gaza-war-israel-palestine-war-narendra-modi-explained-why-israel-gaza-war-is-a-diplomatic-test-for-india-4463674%5C%22%3EExplained%3A%20Why%20Israel-Gaza%20War%20Is%20A%20Diplomatic%20Test%20For%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Hamas%20militants%20began%20their%20assault%2C%20panic-stricken%20Israelis%20hid%20in%20their%20homes%20with%20reports%20rife%20that%20Hamas%20was%20carrying%20out%20terrorist%20attacks%20going%20door-to-door%2C%20shooting%20civilians%20or%20dragging%20them%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHalf%20a%20century%20after%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%201973%20Arab-Israeli%20War%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20informed%20a%20shocked%20nation%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20war.%26quot%3B%20The%20Israeli%20leader%20vowed%20to%20turn%20Hamas%20hideouts%20%26quot%3Bto%20rubble%26quot%3B%20and%20urged%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20to%20%26quot%3Bflee%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20hard%20to%20witness%20the%20helplessness%20of%20civilians%2C%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20many%20elderly%20people%20and%20children%20being%20slaughtered%20in%20their%20homes%20or%20kidnapped%2C%20hundreds%20of%20young%20party-goers%20butchered%20at%20gunpoint%20by%20Islamist%20terrorists%20who%20take%20pride%20in%20their%20subhuman%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Zakh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas'%20large-scale%20attack%20has%20killed%20at%20least%20700%20and%20wounded%201%2C200%20Israelis.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20at%20least%20100%20Israeli%20citizens%20have%20been%20captured%20by%20Hamas%20and%20taken%20to%20Gaza%2C%20with%20shocking%20images%20circulating%20online%20of%20bloodied%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sights%20and%20sounds%20were%20of%20a%20scale%20that%20reminded%20us%20of%20what%20we%20know%20from%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20and%20never%20ever%20forget.%20A%20feeling%20of%20extreme%20rage%20ensued%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Zakh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Foqsa39l8_jerusalem-afp-_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20onslaught%20subsided%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20unleashed%20their%20fury%20and%20pounded%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20intensifying%20their%20bombardment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Zakh%2C%20after%20spending%20around%2020%20years%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20a%20PhD%20in%20computer%20science%20at%20Ben-Gurion%20University.%20Two%20days%20after%20the%20shock%20attacks%2C%20staring%20at%20empty%20streets%20and%20contemplating%20the%20future%20of%20his%20war-torn%20country%2C%20Mr%20Zakh%20hopes%20for%20a%20change%20in%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20as%20the%20war%20unfolds%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20status%20quo%20in%20which%20genocidal%20Islamist%20entities%20are%20allowed%20to%20thrive%20at%20our%20doorstep%2C%20be%20it%20in%20Gaza%20or%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20accepted.%20This%20equation%20must%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20insists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20remains%20the%20hope%20of%20not%20just%20Mr%20Zakh%2C%20but%20also%20thousands%20of%20Israelis%20who%20have%20either%20lost%20someone%20in%20the%20attacks%20or%20are%20now%20actively%20part%20of%20their%20country's%20retaliation%20efforts.%20But%20as%20things%20stand%2C%20both%20sides%20continue%20to%20lose%20blood%20with%20the%20war%20not%20expected%20to%20end%20any%20time%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696843380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F0md40pbo_alaqsa-mosque-afp-_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-hamas-mossad-gaza-ndtv-exclusive-ex-soldier-re