m%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20of%20Power%20Producers%20wrote%20to%20the%20coal%20ministry%20in%20November%202021%20to%20open%20up%20for%20auctions%20two%20coal%20blocks%20nestled%20in%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20densest%20forests%20to%20address%20the%20rumoured%20coal%20shortage%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20the%20lobbying%20was%20poised%20to%20benefit%20its%20member%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20two%20blocks%20the%20Association%20lobbied%20for%20is%20situated%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Singrauli%20coalfields%20and%20is%20close%20to%20a%20thermal%20power%20plant%20the%20Adani%20Group%20acquired%20in%20March%202022.%20The%20other%2C%20situated%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20pristine%20Hasdeo%20Arand%20forests%2C%20is%20adjacent%20to%20blocks%20mined%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20coal%20ministry%20not%20only%20acted%20on%20the%20association%E2%80%99s%20demand%20to%20open%20up%20the%20two%20blocks%20but%20went%20a%20step%20ahead%20and%20pushed%20for%20a%20review%20of%20the%20environment%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20suggestions%20in%202018%20that%2015%20coal%20blocks%2C%20which%20includes%20one%20of%20the%20two%2C%20should%20be%20exempt%20from%20coal%20mining%20auctions%20since%20they%20fall%20in%20areas%20that%20have%20high%20biodiversity%20value%20and%20need%20to%20be%20conserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20the%20review%2C%20the%20coal%20ministry%20tasked%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Mine%20Planning%20and%20Design%20Institute%20(CMPDI)%20to%20see%20if%20portions%20of%20these%2015%20blocks%20could%20be%20carved%20out%20to%20allow%20mining%20without%20disturbing%20the%20forests.%20The%20Institute%2C%20affiliated%20with%20the%20coal%20ministry%2C%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cspecialist%20consultant%20for%20all%20those%20in%20the%20mineral%20and%20mining%20sector%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%2C%20in%20its%20presentation%2C%2