ich%20will%20take%20place%20Nov.%2024-Dec.%202.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Chastain%20was%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20Venice%20Film%20Festival%20for%20Michel%20Franco%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%E2%80%9CMemory%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20received%20an%20interim%20waiver%20from%20SAG-AFTRA.%20Succeeding%20to%20Paolo%20Sorrentino%2C%20Chastain%20will%20lead%20the%20jury%20of%20the%20competition%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fjessica-chastain-jury-marrakech-film-festival-1235748970%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fjessica-chastain-jury-marrakech-film-festival-1235748970%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fjessica-chastain-jury-marrakech-film-festival-1235748970%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NewsClick%20Raids%20and%20Arrests%3A%20Demolishing%20the%20Myth%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal'%20Nomenclature%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09131528%2Fnewsclick-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20search%20and%20seizure%20operation%20at%20the%20residences%20of%2046%20journalists%20associated%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-conducts-early-morning-raids-at-houses-of-journalists-satirists%5C%22%3Earrests%20of%20two%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20transparently%20part%20of%20the%20same%20politics%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20invention%20of%20the%20still%20ambiguous%20phrases%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etukde-tukde%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20gang%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESohail%20Hashmi%2C%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20D.%20Raghunandan%20and%20Urmilesh%20are%20my%20JNU%20contemporaries%20of%20the%201970s-1980s.%20Abhisar%20Sharma%20invited%20me%20to%20NDTV%20to%20discuss%20Naxalism%20and%20Indian%20politics%20a%20few%20times%20and%20I%20interacted%20with%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%20in%20seminars.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20friend%20since%201973%2C%20Sohail%20Hashmi%20and%20I%20resided%20in%20the%20newly-constructed%20Kaveri%20hostel%20at%20JNU.%C2%A0%20From%20a%20leftist%20freedom%20fighter%20family%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Students%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20our%20political%20convictions%20differed.%20Yet%2C%20a%20rewardingly%20amalgamating%20political%20atmosphere%20brought%20most%20of%20us%20together.%20Political%20lines%20did%20not%20matter%20even%20during%20the%20JNU%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20(JNUSU)%20elections.%20His%20transformation%20into%20a%20cultural%20historian%20post-JNU%20and%20his%20activism%20under%20SAHMAT%20with%20sister%20Shabnam%20continue.%20However%2C%20his%20being%20part%20of%20any%20anti-national%20activity%20is%20as%20much%20true%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EKabir%2C%20Guru%20Nanak%20Dev%20and%20Baba%20Gorakhnath%20discoursing%20spirituality%20together!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrabir%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPurkayastha%20was%20also%20a%20prominent%20student%20activist%20of%20the%20SFI%20at%20the%20JNU%20campus.%20A%20cultured%20soft-spoken%2C%20ever-smiling%20personality%2C%20his%20ideology%20never%20came%20between%20personal%20friendship%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum.%20He%20was%20a%20remarkably%20motivating%20speaker%20whenever%20we%20gathered%20to%20discuss%20national%20or%20international%20politics.%20I%20vividly%20remember%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fprofessor-gyan-prakash-emergency-totalitarianism-prabir-purkayastha%5C%22%3Ekidnap-style%20arrest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20front%20of%20the%20School%20of%20Languages%20building%20on%20the%20old%20campus%20on%20September%2025%2C%201975%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20An%20Ambassador%20car%20driven%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20henchman%20DIG%20P.S.%20Bhinder%20himself%20stopped%20near%20him%20and%20he%20was%20dragged%20in.%20As%20he%20was%20driven%20off%2C%20the%20late%20Professor%20K.%20Seshadri%20of%20the%20CPS%20lunged%20forward%20but%20the%20car%20raced%20past%20him%2C%20all%20but%20running%20him%20over.%20But%20despite%20the%20allegations%20about%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-case-no-foreign-funding-neville-roy-singham-company-statement%5C%22%3Efunding%20from%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20being%20part%20of%20any%20anti-India%20design%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20any%20myth%20passed%20on%20as%20history%20today.%C2%A0%20In%20the%20late%201980s%2C%20we%20met%20once%20a%20month%20at%20the%20Vasant%20Valley%20School%20where%20our%20children%20went.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EK.%20Raghunandan%2C%20an%20aeronautical%20engineer%20from%20the%20Rolls%2C%20who%20came%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Social%20Systems%20to%20do%20an%20M.Phil%20in%201977%2C%20is%20the%20director%20of%20Delhi%20Science%20Forum%20and%20is%20engaged%20in%20Innovation%20Technology.%20My%20personal%20contacts%20with%20him%20have%20been%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20He%20was%20an%20SFI%20member%20and%20was%20elected%20president%20of%20JNUSU.%20I%20would%20really%20be%20shocked%20if%20the%20charges%20of%20anti-national%20activities%20against%20him%20are%20proven.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUrmilesh%20was%20several%20years%20my%20junior.%20I%20remember%20him%20as%20an%20unassuming%2C%20smiling%2C%20soft%20personality.%C2%A0%20Our%20meetings%20post-JNU%20were%20in%20academic%20or%20social%20gatherings.%20As%20a%20Hindi%20journalist%2C%20he%20has%20remained%20a%20prolific%20writer%20with%20substance%20and%20style%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20ever%20write%20anything%20that%20could%20be%20called%20treason.%20We%20also%20shared%20a%20dais%20on%20panel%20discussions%20a%20few%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20any%20of%20these%20or%20the%2040-odd%20others%20be%20termed%20an%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99%3F%20Far%20from%20it.%20But%20let%20me%20also%20demolish%20the%20myth%20of%20this%20nomenclature.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134247%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.11-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134247%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.11-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134247%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.11-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05134247%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-05-at-1.39.11-PM-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678407%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20protest%20against%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20swoop%20on%20journalists%20and%20others%20associated%20with%20NewsClick%2C%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%2C%20October%204%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Yaqut%20Ali%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFrom%20Naxalism%20to%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99%3A%20the%20incongruities%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20new%20category%20of%20dissenters%2C%20deprecated%20as%20anti-nationals%2C%20is%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20This%20came%20into%20use%20since%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%20in%202018.%20A%20meeting%20of%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20lawyers%20and%20others%20in%20Pune%20on%20December%2031%2C%202017%2C%20known%20as%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20and%20meant%20to%20commemorate%20the%20bicentenary%20of%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20battle%2C%20turned%20into%20a%20pretext%20to%20round%20up%20a%20number%20of%20%E2%80%98leftist%E2%80%99%20activists%20under%20the%20draconian%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(UAPA).%20Several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhima-koregaon-16-must-not-be-forgotten%5C%22%3Econtinue%20to%20be%20imprisoned%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20today.%20Since%20they%20had%20defended%20persons%20falsely%20implicated%20of%20being%20Naxals%2C%20the%20invented%20incongruous%20nomenclature%20of%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99%20is%20given%20to%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20incongruous%20because%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98Naxal%E2%80%99%20was%20used%20without%20an%20understanding%20of%20what%20Naxalims%20is.%C2%A0%20Let%20me%20use%20my%20two%20research%20papers%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchiv.ub.uni-heidelberg.de%2Fvolltextserver%2F8710%2F%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Experiment%20with%20Revolution%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcollections.unu.edu%2Feserv%2FUNU%3A2507%2Febrary9789280811940.pdf%5C%22%3EOld%20Revolution%2C%20New%20Context%3A%20Maoism%20in%20a%20Globalizing%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20explain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20latter%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20B.%20Sudershan%20Reddy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fjonew%2Fjudis%2F38160.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESalwa%20Judum%3C%2Fem%3E%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%202011%20to%20highlight%20the%20socio-economic%20inequalities%20that%20led%20to%20%E2%80%98Naxalism%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20brief%2C%20the%20attempted%20Marxist-Maoist%20%E2%80%98revolution%E2%80%99%20began%20in%201946%20in%20Telangana%2C%20died%20there%20in%201951%20due%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhoodan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20movement%20by%20Acharya%20Vinoba%20Bhave%2C%20re-emerged%20in%201967%20in%20Naxalbari%20(hence%20Naxalism)%20village%20in%20north%20West%20Bengal%2C%20was%20crushed%20there%20by%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%201970s%2C%20sprouted%20in%20Srikakulam%20(Andhra%20Pradesh)%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20spread%20further%20from%20there.%20And%20gradually%20between%20the%201980s%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20millennium%2C%20when%20the%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20was%20formed%20(2003)%2C%20it%20affected%20over%20200%20of%20over%20600%20districts%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(undivided)%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(undivided)%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Odisha.%20I%20identified%20three%20root%20causes%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98revolution%E2%80%99%3A%20(i)%20development%20deficit%2C%20(ii)%20development%20dichotomy%20and%20(iii)%20displacement-rehabilitation%20hiatus.%20The%20conflict%20for%20land%20and%20resources%20has%20been%20at%20the%20root%20of%20the%20grassroots%20support%20and%20its%20expansion%20in%20the%20country.%20Even%20the%20erstwhile%20Planning%20Commission%20study%20(2006)%20pointed%20to%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20a%20brief%20attempt%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20it%20never%20had%20an%20urban%20impact.%20However%2C%20the%20urban%20Marxist%20intelligentsia%20did%20work%20for%20the%20defence%20of%20those%20tribal%20and%20rural%20citizens%20who%20were%20caught%20in%20the%20collateral%20zone%20and%20were%20harassed%20and%20arrested%20by%20the%20police.%20The%20Indian%20state%20since%202014%20turned%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eastringent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20this%20intellectual%20support%20base%20consisting%20of%20lawyers%2C%20journalists%2C%20university%20teachers%2C%20civil%20rights%20activists%20and%20social%20workers.%C2%A0%20Since%20this%20section%20also%20opposed%20the%20saffron%20politics%2C%20they%20were%20dubbed%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxals%E2%80%99%2C%20incongruities%20therein%20notwithstanding.%20Even%20though%20this%20disconsonant%20term%20has%20not%20been%20used%2C%20the%20methodology%20of%20the%20current%20crack-down%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20brief%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20this%20nomenclature%20is%20used%2C%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20is%20working%20on%20these%20lines.%20However%2C%20a%20case%20against%20any%20of%20these%20people%20for%20being%20either%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edeshdrohi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20an%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99%20is%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EAjay%20K.%20Mehra%20is%20a%20political%20scientist.%20He%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Senior%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202019-21%20and%20Principal%2C%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Evening%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University%20(2018).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696840167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09131528%2Fnewsclick-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-and-arrests-demolishing-the-myth-of-the-urban-naxal-nomenclature%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20current%20crackdown%20is%20transparently%20part%20of%20the%20same%20politics%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20invention%20of%20ambiguous%20phrases%20like%20'tukde-tukde%20gang'%20and%20%E2%80%98Urban%20Naxal%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fnewsclick-raids-and-arrests-demolishing-the-myth-of-the-urban-naxal-nomenclature%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%E2%