%3Cspan%3EThe%20UAE%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-israel-uae-palestine-donald-trump-jaishankar%5C%22%3Ewhich%20had%20normalised%20ties%20with%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%2C%20has%20also%20been%20part%20of%20this%20stream%20of%20phone%20conversations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UAE%20foreign%20ministry%20stated%20that%20Zayed%20held%20phone%20conversations%20with%20the%20king%20of%20Jordan%2C%20the%20presidents%20of%20Egypt%2C%20Syria%20and%20Israel%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Canada%20on%20the%20latest%20Israel-Palestinian%20violence%20on%20Sunday%20(October%208).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20UAE%20readout%20mentioned%20the%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cde-escalate%E2%80%9D%20and%20exercise%20maximum%20restraint%20so%20that%20the%20region%20does%20not%20enter%20a%20new%20crisis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Canadian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pm.gc.ca%2Fen%2Fnews%2Freadouts%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fprime-minister-justin-trudeau-speaks-president-united-arab-emirates-his%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereadout%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20said%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20spoke%20about%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20attack%20on%20Israel.%20It%20added%20another%20detail%2C%20which%20was%20not%20mentioned%20by%20the%20UAE%2C%20saying%20that%20Trudeau%20%E2%80%9Cprovided%20an%20update%20on%20the%20situation%20between%20Canada%20and%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhow-countries-across-the-world-reacted-to-hamas-attack-and-israel-palestine-war%5C%22%3ECeasefire%20Call%20Amidst%20Condemnation%3A%20World%20Reacts%20to%20Hamas%20Offensive%20and%20Israeli%20Airstrikes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrudeau%E2%80%99s%20tweet%20elaborated%20that%20on%20India%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20spoke%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20importance%20of%20upholding%20%E2%80%93%20and%20respecting%20%E2%80%93%20the%20rule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20phone%20today%2C%20His%20Highness%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMohamedBinZayed%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MohamedBinZayed%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20I%20spoke%20about%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Israel.%20We%20expressed%20our%20deep%20concern%20and%20discussed%20the%20need%20to%20protect%20civilian%20life.%20We%20also%20spoke%20about%20India%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20upholding%20%E2%80%93%20and%20respecting%20%E2%80%93%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Justin%20Trudeau%20(%40JustinTrudeau)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJustinTrudeau%2Fstatus%2F1711062473971810740%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Canadian%20PM%20also%20had%20a%20phone%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FJustinTrudeau%2Fstatus%2F1711073870822679009%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJordanian%20King%20Abdullah%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20that%20the%20dispute%20with%20India%20was%20raised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticle-read-statements-from-the-prime-minister-and-opposition-leaders-on%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Canada%20made%20an%20explosive%20allegation%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20national%20who%20had%20been%20charged%20as%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20terrorist%20by%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20angrily%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%E2%80%9D%