pective%20of%20their%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Asha%20was%20recognised%20at%20a%20State%20Level%20Teacher%20Award%20Ceremony%20by%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20for%20her%20work.%20She%20was%20also%20conferred%20the%20Ambedkar%20Mahila%20Puraskar%20Award%202023.%20This%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%20on%20September%205%2C%20she%20was%20awarded%20the%20National%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Award%202023%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20recognition%2C%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20training%20young%20girls%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20is%20paramount%20for%20Asha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20this%20work%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20personal%20happiness.%20Now%2C%20I%20sleep%20peacefully%20knowing%20the%20girls%20I%20trained%20will%20be%20able%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20the%20humiliation%20that%20was%20once%20caused%20to%20one%20of%20my%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F1679310394CII2021Volume1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECrime%20In%20India%202021%20Volume%20I%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3EBy%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs)%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Asha%20Suman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696603084000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAsha-Suman-1-1696597320.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alwar's%20Asha%20Suman%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20imparting%20self-defence%20skills%20to%20young%20girls.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20trained%2030%2C000%20girls%20across%20Rajasthan.%20This%20Teacher%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C