20Such%20is%20the%20story%20of%20many%20people%20with%20the%20rare%2C%20progressive%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20when%2014-month-old%20Roha%20began%20experiencing%20trouble%20breathing%2C%20her%20parents%20rushed%20her%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20another%20town.%20After%20two%20weeks%2C%20multiple%20tests%20and%20misdiagnoses%20later%2C%20they%20were%20shattered%20to%20know%20that%20their%20little%20daughter%20had%20the%20fatal%20illness.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20they%20heard%20of%20SMA%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20it%20meant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20(RPwD%20Act%2C%202016)%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20include%20SMA%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20not%20much%20awareness%20of%20the%20condition%20even%20among%20medical%20professionals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKaran%20Shah%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20canine%20and%20feline%20behaviourist%2C%20was%20misdiagnosed%20with%20polio%20shortly%20after%20birth.%20However%2C%20he%20got%20a%20diagnosis%20after%20his%20mother%20insisted%20on%20getting%20him%20tested%20for%20the%20condition.%20He%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20Pawsitivve%20Future%2C%20a%20canine%20training%20centre%2C%20and%20lives%20with%20SMA%20Type-III.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20such%20a%20drastic%20impact%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20get%20to%20know%20more%20about%20this%20condition%20that%20creates%20significant%20impairment%20and%20results%20in%20a%20locomotor%20disability.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295507%2Fdisability-inclusive-policy-at-workplaces-lessons-from-accenture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAwareness%20is%20the%20first%20step%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20the%20cause%20in%20various%20capacities%2C%20including%20raising%20funds%20for%20its%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201075px)%20100vw%2C%201075px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20there's%20no%20cure%20for%20SMA%2C%20several%20treatments%20have%20been%20suggested%20to%20make%20the%20condition%20less%20disabling%20for%20those%20who%20live%20with%20it.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168.jpg%201075w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fshutterstock_2170103803_11zon-2-1696513168-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331649%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22716%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20cure%20for%20SMA%2C%20several%20treatments%20have%20been%20suggested%20to%20make%20the%20condition%20less%20disabling%20for%20those%20who%20live%20with%20it.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20SMA%20and%20whom%20does%20it%20affect%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESMA%20is%20a%20genetic%20condition%20that%20impacts%20the%20control%20of%20muscle%20movement.%20It%20mainly%20affects%20the%20spinal%20region%20while%20the%20muscles%20of%20peripheral%20internal%20organs%20are%20relatively%20unaffected.%20SMA%20is%20a%20progressive%20condition%20that%20ultimately%20leads%20to%20muscle%20wastage%20or%20atrophy%20in%20the%20body.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20globally%2C%201%20in%20every%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnceh%2Fdls%2Fnsmbb_sma.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSpinal%2520Muscular%2520Atrophy%2520(SMA)%2520is%2Cbeing%2520unable%2520to%2520make%2520protein.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10%2C000%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20SMA%2C%20while%20in%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asterhospitals.in%2Fblogs-events-news%2Faster-cmi-bangalore%2Fspinal-muscular-atrophy-types-symptoms-and-treatment%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSMA%2520is%2520a%2520relatively%2520rare%2Caround%25203%252C200%2520newborns%2520every%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3%2C200%20infants%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20born%20with%20the%20condition%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mda.org%2Fdisease%2Fspinal-muscular-atrophy%2Fcauses-inheritance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMuscular%20Dystrophy%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SMA%20is%20caused%20by%20missing%20or%20mutated%20SMN1%20or%20SMN2%20genes%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20survival%20muscle%20neuron%20genes.%20The%20protein%20produced%20by%20this%20gene%20%E2%80%94%20SMN%20protein%20%E2%80%94%20facilitates%20movement%20and%20is%20needed%20by%20motor%20neurons%20to%20function%20effectively.%20Since%20the%20gene%20is%20faulty%20or%20missing%2C%20it%20impedes%20movement%20among%20those%20who%20are%20affected%20by%20SMA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindividuals%20experience%20several%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20voluntary%20movements%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20the%20head%2C%20neck%2C%20and%20limbs.%20Priya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20spinal%20cord%20and%20the%20surrounding%20areas%20are%20affected%2C%20people%20with%20SMA%20also%20develop%20scoliosis%20or%20spinal%20curvature.%20I%20have%20it%20too%20and%20I%20manage%20it%20by%20stuffing%20a%20lot%20of%20cushions%20around%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20limited%20mobility%2C%20I%20have%20low%20muscle%20tone%20which%20results%20in%20weaker%20bone%20health%20and%20density.%20Even%20lifting%20a%20book%20seems%20like%20a%20Herculean%20task%20to%20me.%20My%20condition%20also%20makes%20me%20prone%20to%20frequent%20fractures%20and%20joint%20dislocations.%20Since%20my%20mobility%20is%20impacted%2C%20I%20use%20a%20wheelchair%20to%20move%20around%20and%20need%20support%20with%20activities%20of%20daily%20living.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20Priya%2C%20many%20others%20with%20SMA%20require%20wheelchairs%20too.%20They%20may%20also%20rely%20on%20different%20support%20needs%20for%20daily%20life.%20Some%20patients%20have%20difficulty%20in%20swallowing%20and%20eating%20food%20and%20may%20require%20a%20feeding%20tube%20while%20others%20with%20compromised%20lungs%20may%20need%20breathing%20support%20or%20ventilation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-300x175.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-500x292.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-768x448.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FSMA-1-1696513914-150x88.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331662%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Priya%2C%20her%20caregiver%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20my%20parents%20have%20aged%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20them%20to%20lift%20me%20up%2C%20carry%20me%20around%20or%20support%20my%20needs.%20If%20my%20caregiver%20goes%20on%20a%20leave%20for%20even%20one%20day%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20my%20mother%20and%20even%20the%20most%20basic%20of%20everyday%20activities%20seem%20impossible.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20recounts%20how%20there%20have%20been%20times%20when%20people%20give%20unsolicited%20advice%20to%20her%20and%20her%20family%20about%20managing%20her%20disability%20without%20realising%20none%20of%20them%20work%20because%20her%20body%20functions%20differently%20than%20other%20people%E2%80%99s.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20while%20travelling%20in%20a%20car%20or%20plane%2C%20someone%20must%20hold%20me%20tightly%20because%20even%20the%20slightest%20of%20jerks%20can%20make%20me%20fall%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Alpana%20Sharma%2C%20caring%20for%20her%2011-year-old%20son%20Aarav%2C%20who%20has%20SMA%20Type-II%2C%20has%20been%20an%20exhausting%20process.%20With%20managing%20doctors%E2%80%99%20appointments%2C%20therapy%20and%20everything%20else%20that%20comes%20along%20with%20the%20journey%2C%20the%20mother%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20days%20when%20I%20thought%20%E2%80%98why%20me%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20stigma%20of%20a%20genetic%20condition%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20our%20friends%20cut%20ties%20with%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20festive%20celebration%2C%20Alpana%20recounts%2C%20a%20woman%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20her%20child%20eat%20the%20%3Cem%3Eprasad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(food%20offered%20to%20a%20deity)%20being%20distributed%20by%20Aarav%2C%20in%20fear%20of%20contacting%20SMA%20from%20him.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20one%20cannot