nitoring%20dietary%20intake%2C%20or%20surgical%20interventions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20accessibility%20of%20medical%20care%20for%20SMA%2C%20Priya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20SMA%20is%20a%20genetic%20condition%2C%20the%20availability%20of%20gene%20replacement%20therapy%20is%20like%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20in%20darkness.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20extremely%20costly%20which%20makes%20it%20inaccessible.%20One-time%20infusion%20costs%20anywhere%20from%20a%20whopping%20Rs%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F04%2F06%2Fbusiness%2Findia-spinal-muscular-atrophy.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E65%20lakh%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-livemint-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fv%2Fs%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fscience%2Fnews%2Fzolgensma-the-world-s-most-expensive-drug-costs-rs-18-crore-per-dose-5-points%2Famp-11615253464861.html%3Famp_gsa%3D1%26amp_js_v%3Da9%26usqp%3Dmq331AQIUAKwASCAAgM%253D%23amp_tf%3DFrom%2520%25251%2524s%26aoh%3D16898371078147%26referrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%26ampshare%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.livemint.com%252Fscience%252Fnews%252Fzolgensma-the-world-s-most-expensive-drug-costs-rs-18-crore-per-dose-5-points-11615253464861.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E18%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20these%20costs%20are%20not%20covered%20under%20medical%20insurance%2C%20we%20often%20have%20to%20resort%20to%20crowdfunding%2C%20or%20in%20the%20worst%20case%20scenario%2C%20see%20a%20life%20slipping%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10104684%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D100%2525%2520of%2520the%2520patients%2520who%2Cdrug%2520for%2520SMA%2520Type%25201.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20shown%20that%20those%20who%20recei