28%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHe%20has%20managed%20to%20collect%20and%20preserve%20500%20%2B%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20rice%20varieties.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Mahan%20Borah%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMahan%20started%20to%20visit%20more%20farms%20in%20Assam%20and%20learnt%20about%20the%20types%20of%20seeds%20they%20sow%20and%20managed%20to%20collect%20more%20and%20more%20seeds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20library%20is%20also%20a%20gene%20bank%20of%20indigenous%20seeds%20that%20are%20fast%20disappearing%20not%20only%20from%20Assam%20but%20also%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20northeast%20India%3B%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20as%20well.%20We%20have%20various%20varieties%20of%20rice%20such%20as%20Bhao%20Dhan%20which%20has%20a%20cooling%20effect%20on%20the%20body%2C%20Dol%20Kosu%20which%20can%20treat%20fever%20and%20Navara%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rice%20variety%20from%20Kerala%20which%20has%20medicinal%20properties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMahan%E2%80%99s%20seed%20library%20boasts%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20rice%20seeds%20that%20are%20aromatic%2C%20sticky%2C%20black%2C%20flood-tolerant%20and%20hill%20rice%2C%20even%20some%20with%20medicinal%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20personal%20favourite%20type%20of%20rice%2C%20Mahan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20all%20these%20rice%20varieties%20are%20my%20favourite%2C%20Bhao%20Dhan%20is%20very%20good.%20It%20is%20very%20tough%20in%20nature%20and%20can%20adapt%20easily%20to%20the%20flood-prone%20nature%20of%20Assam.%20It%20can%20survive%20long%20periods%20of%20being%20submerged%20in%20water.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20lower%20yield%20per%20hectare%20has%20been%20a%20factor%20as%20the%20farmers%20do%20not%20prefer%20to%20grow%20the%20rice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20believe%20that%20such%20varieties%20need%20to%20be%20saved.%20They%20were%20grown%20and%20consumed%20by%20our%20forefathers%20before%20farming%20was%20commercialised.%20They%20are%20the%20legacy%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20protected%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mahan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20his%20cause%20further%2C%20Mahan%20says%20that%20his%20library%20is%20open%20for%20anyone%20to%20visit%20and%20take%20seeds%20of%20the%20rice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fseed-library-3-1696513497.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fseed-library-3-1696513497.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fseed-library-3-1696513497-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fseed-library-3-1696513497-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fseed-library-3-1696513497-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fseed-library-3-1696513497-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20library%20also%20has%20records%20of%20information%20about%20each%20variety%20and%20how%20they%20can%20be%20grown.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Mahan%20Borah%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFarmers%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291959%2Fbest-products-from-northeast-india-sustainable-startup-entrepreneurs-small-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enortheastern%20parts%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20to%20the%20library%20and%20they%20are%20free%20to%20take%20the%20seeds%20and%20try%2