20a%20small%20human.%20Some%20mothers%20find%20pregnancy%20difficult%2C%20others%20have%20a%20traumatic%20labour%20and%20delivery%2C%20and%20some%20struggle%20during%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326043%2Ftwo-moms-serve-the-magic-of-home-cooked-eco-friendly-dabbas-to-thousands-in-london%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20postpartum%20period%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Pooja%20Srinivasa%20Raja%2C%20it%20was%20the%20latter.%20After%20a%20smooth%20pregnancy%20and%20delivery%2C%20the%20then%2022-year-old%20was%20hit%20hard%20by%20postpartum%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20felt%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20my%20baby%20or%20the%20pregnancy%20or%20delivery.%20I%20felt%20very%20low.%20People%20would%20come%20and%20make%20unkind%20comments%20about%20my%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20appearance.%20They%20would%20say%20that%20she%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20facial%20hair%2C%20she%20is%20dark%2C%20etc.%20This%20really%20triggered%20me%20and%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20trauma%20I%20went%20through%20growing%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pooja%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20went%20through%20a%20very%20low%20phase%20for%20the%20first%20four%20months%20after%20childbirth.%20She%20recalls%20crying%20without%20a%20clear%20reason.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%20not%20okay.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20sleeping%2C%20and%20I%20was%20unsure%20about%20my%20career.%20Seeing%20my%20friends%20studying%20or%20working%20on%20social%20media%20led%20me%20further%20down%20the%20spiral.%20After%20three%20months%20postpartum%2C%20I%20started%20having%20suicidal%20thoughts%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now%2027-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20night%2C%20she%20poured%20out%20her%20feelings%20to%20her%20mother%20and%20cried.%20Her%20mother%20suggested%20that%20she%20should%20start%20therapy%2C%20which%20effectively%20turned%20around%20Pooja%E2%80%9