20restaurants.%20%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20joint%20family%2C%20but%20I%20never%20shared%20what%20I%20was%20going%20through%20with%20anyone.%20I%20just%20thought%20that%20there%20was%20something%20wrong%20with%20me.%20I%20had%20low%20self-esteem.%20We%20are%20always%20told%2C%20as%20women%2C%20that%20we%20must%20look%20a%20certain%20way%20and%20dress%20a%20certain%20way.%20We%20are%20told%20that%20we%20must%20adjust%20and%20compromise.%20Today%2C%20I%20realise%20how%20important%20it%20is%20for%20us%20to%20talk%20and%20voice%20out%20our%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20it%20took%20about%20one%20to%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20therapy%20for%20her%20to%20feel%20better%20and%20improve%20her%20sleep%20patterns.%20When%20she%20started%20speaking%20to%20her%20friends%20about%20going%20to%20therapy%2C%20they%20would%20ask%20her%20why%20she%20was%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCs0MZy6SHKg%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCs0MZy6SHKg%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCs0MZy6SHKg%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%20%7C%20Mental%20health%20(%40thelovehopecompany)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20awareness%20about%20mental%20health.%20We%20are%20always%20expected%20to%20fit%20into%20societal%20norms.%20Most%20of%20us%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20follow%20our%20passion.%20Till%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20would%20have%20never%20thought%20that%20I%20would%20be%20starting%20a%20mental%20health%20space.%20Conversations%20with%20my%20friends%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20more%20talk%20on%20mental%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajesh%2C%20a%20Mumbai%20resident%2C%20vouches%20for%20the%20role%20that%20therapy%20plays%20in%20improving%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CI%20lost%20my%20job%20and%20my%20father%20during%20COVID.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20lowest%20phase%20of%20my%20life%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20to%20turn%20to%20for%20help.%20I%20just%20stayed%20home%20for%20almost%2045%20days%20without%20even%20stepping%20foot%20outside.%20When%20speaking%20to%20my%20children%2C%20friends%20and%20family%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work%2C%20my%20wife%20urged%20me%20to%20try%20therapy.%20I%20scoffed%2C%20but%20she%20insisted%20I%20take%20an%20online%20session.%20It%20really%20helped.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20realise%20many%20more%20things%20about%20myself%20and%20I%20am%20able%20to%20deal%20with%20my%20failures%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20stigma%20around%20mental%20health.%20To%20bridge%20that%20gap%2C%20in%202019%2C%20she%20started%20an%20NGO%20called%20Transfomind%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%20platform%20to%20create%20awareness%20of%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20collaborated%20with%20mental%20health%20experts%20to%20develop%20educational%20material%20on%20mental%20well-being.%20This%20idea%20gained%20traction%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20raising%20significant%20awareness.%20In%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20teamed%20up%20with%20Montfort%20College%20to%20offer%20free%20therapy%20sessions%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20a%20challenging%20time%20in%20Pooja%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life%20as%20she%20was%20separated%20from%20her%20husband.%20During%20a%20solo%20trip%2C%20a%20conversation%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health%20ignited%20the%20fire%20in%20the%2027-year-old%20to%20do%20something%20more%20concrete%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20little%20bit%20of%20love%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20hope%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20therapy%20spaces%20at%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331556%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGrou