itle%20of%20%3Cem%3EBhakt%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20kind%20of%20honorific%20at%20that%20time)%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20was%20no%20less%20than%20any%20award.%20Alongside%20this%20work%2C%20he%20used%20to%20sell%20milk%2C%20curd%2C%20%3Cem%3Emisri%20%3C%2Fem%3E(rock%20sugar)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emawa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(dried%20whole%20milk).%20At%20that%20time%2C%20these%20sweets%20were%20the%20trend%20and%20were%20largely%20in%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%20to%20inform%20that%20once%20when%20Parmanand%20Jain%20was%20slow-boiling%20the%20milk%2C%20he%20accidentally%20reduced%20it%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20he%20invited%20his%20wrestler%20friends%20to%20taste%20the%20sweet%2C%20they%20were%20in%20awe.%20Thereafter%2C%20Parmanand%20Jain%20started%20making%20%3Cem%3Erabri%20%3C%2Fem%3Eregularly%20and%20soon%20after%2C%20it%20became%20a%20must-have%20in%20royal%20feasts%20and%20special%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20Mahaveer%20Rabri%20Bhandar%20came%20to%20be%20in%201857.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeepak%20elaborates%20that%20Jain%20continued%20to%20run%20the%20shop%20for%2060%20years%20before%20his%20sons%20took%20over.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20three%20sons%3A%20Dasulal%20Jain%2C%20Kapurchand%20Jain%2C%20and%20Mohanlal%20Jain.%20All%20three%20brothers%20were%20into%20%3Cem%3Epehalwani%20%3C%2Fem%3E(wrestling)%20but%20only%20Kapurchandji%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecould%20achieve%20great%20fame.%20He%20was%20the%20head%20of%20all%2054%20%3Cem%3Eakhara%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(wrestling%20grounds)%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20earned%20the%20title%20of%20%3Cem%3EUstaad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Master).%20He%20dedicated%20his%20entire%20life%20to%20wrestling%20and%20ran%20the%20business%20as%20well.%20It%20is%20because%20of%20him%20that%20we%20earned%20so%20much%20fame%20worldwide%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fr